Note: Additional path builder operations
Process reset_path_builder with builder as PathBuilder:
    Set builder.current_path to create_empty_canvas_path
    Set builder.current_point to core.create_vector2d with x as 0.0 and y as 0.0
    Set builder.path_closed to false

Process add_move_to_segment with builder as PathBuilder and point as core.Vector2D:
    Set builder.current_point to point
    Note: Add move-to segment to current path

