Process add_bezier_curve_segment with builder as PathBuilder and control1 as core.Vector2D and control2 as core.Vector2D and end as core.Vector2D:
    Set builder.current_point to end
    Note: Add bezier curve segment to current path

Process add_arc_segment with builder as PathBuilder and center as core.Vector2D and radius as Float and start as Float and end as Float and ccw as Boolean:
    Note: Add arc segment to current path
